name: Dinari VWO
description: Dinari VWO dShares (VWO.d) represent 1:1 ownership of shares in the Vanguard FTSE Emerging Markets ETF (VWO), one of the most popular ETFs providing exposure to equities in emerging markets such as China, India, and Brazil. Each VWO.d token is fully backed by a corresponding Vanguard ETF share securely held in a transparent and auditable treasury. Dinari uses blockchain technology to make traditional investments in emerging market equities accessible to global investors through fractional ownership, 24/7 trading, instant settlement, and enhanced liquidity.
